|所在地={{ill|lt=Nara Prefecture|Q131287|qid=Q131287|1=Nara Prefecture}}{{ill|lt=Shiki District|Q1155036|qid=Q1155036|1=Shiki District, Nara}}{{ill|lt=Tawaramoto|Q1203159|qid=Q1203159|1=Tawaramoto, Nara}}Miyako, Aza Hoya 60
|祭神={{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Ishikori-dome-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN}}
|社格={{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Shikinaisha|1=Shikinaisha|qid=Q134917286}} (small) candidate shrine<br />former {{ill|lt=village shrine|Q134917284|qid=Q134917284|1=Son-sha}}
|創建=Unknown
